{"tid":1046843,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"冇了最愛，好辛苦","createTime":"2019-03-04T14:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T14:50:40.000Z","uid":239817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ddc33aa1415f5e1843e8915dcb107e7203c5102","tid":1046843,"uid":239817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"感情上，我最大的驕傲不是身邊有幾多異性，唔係女朋友有幾咁樣靚身材正，而是找到一個女朋友，即使身邊有人主動示好，我都願意為了她拒絕所有異性，心入面只得佢，比自己更重要，失去咩也不捨得冇了佢！<br />\n我好愛好愛女友，但就比了壓力佢而令佢選擇離開了我，當我準備追回佢一次時，先發覺機會都冇了。<br />\n好想繼續愛佢，繼續支持佢，繼續陪佢，繼續照顧佢。<br />\n我可以點？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/220245_b1bdbf5a74138ea3d101ecba33235256.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F220245_b1bdbf5a74138ea3d101ecba33235256.png&h=a1835ee5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3235ee104db14f915426717ab5b09dbd9750529","tid":1046843,"uid":155197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"做咩影我屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5213e00416c2ca73754931a4298c50bb0f8bcbcc","tid":1046843,"uid":209724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"收皮吧啦"},{"pid":"49b7ec82381822c8aabb874773274e996f49bfae","tid":1046843,"uid":80075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"沒有最愛 只有更愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663914e9e464fdfceecfca2985e685a9b4ec51fa","tid":1046843,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"冇點"},{"pid":"a8df8c56ccbd07309798dacfbdf96248f203606d","tid":1046843,"uid":239817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49b7ec82381822c8aabb874773274e996f49bfae","tid":1046843,"uid":80075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"沒有最愛 只有更愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=